Section 1:
Act 239 of the Regular Session
1 State of Arkansas As Engrossed: S2/19/25
A Bill
2 95th General Assembly
3 Regular Session, 2025 HOUSE BILL 1387
4
5 By: Representative C. Cooper
6 By: Senator J. Payton
7
For An Act To Be Entitled
8
9 AN ACT TO REQUIRE MEMBERS OF THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS
10 OF A PUBLIC WATER AUTHORITY TO PUBLISH THEIR CONTACT
11 INFORMATION UNDER THE WATER AUTHORITY ACT; AND FOR
12 OTHER PURPOSES.
13
14
Subtitle
15
16 TO REQUIRE MEMBERS OF THE BOARD OF
17 DIRECTORS OF A PUBLIC WATER AUTHORITY TO
18 PUBLISH THEIR CONTACT INFORMATION UNDER
19 THE WATER AUTHORITY ACT.
20
21 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
22
23 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code ยง 4-35-204, concerning the board of directors
24 of a public water authority, is amended to add an additional subsection to
25 read as follows:
26 (i)(1)(A) The board of directors of a public water authority shall
27 post contact information on the websites of the public water authority and
28 the Arkansas Natural Resources Commission that are available to the public.
29 (B) As used in subdivision (i)(1)(A) of this section,
30 "contact information" includes the name and telephone number of the member of
31 the board of directors of a public water authority.
32 (2) Any changes to the contact information for a member of the
33 board of directors of a public water authority shall be updated within ten
34 (10) business days.
35
36 APPROVED: 3/4/25
